Also, I think this will be a better example:
```
'''html
<div class="user-container">
  @if (x > y) {
    <b>{{x}}</b> is greater than <b>{{y}}</b>
  } @else if (y > x) {
    <b>{{x}}</b> is less than <b>{{y}}</b>
  } @else {
    <b>{{x}</b>} is equal to <b>{{y}}</b>
  }
</div>
'''
```

because the HTML tags suggest for user that `@if` statement should be used inside `html` file.

